snippet.title: Voice of Vamana   [Teaser Trailer]
snippet.description:
The year is 2130. A vessel from interstellar space - the first concrete proof that humanity is not alone in the universe - has entered our solar system and is hurtling towards our sun. As the only ship capable of reaching it in time, you are tasked with discovering it's purpose. Venture inside the allegedly lifeless thing and divine what you can. From the creator of The Rapture Is Here And You Will Be Forcibly Removed From Your Home.

Voice of Vamana, along with 14 other golden age science fiction games will be available soon at www.antholojam.com/gamesite/
